{"id": "art-911", "label": "Art. 911", "title": "Art. 911: Organizarea şi funcţionarea consorţiilor administrative", "slug": "art-911", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_172107690\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1608\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_172107690\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 91<sup>1</sup>:\nOrganizarea &#351;i func&#355;ionarea consor&#355;iilor administrative </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_604015916\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1607\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_604015916\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Organizarea, func&#355;ionarea &#351;i finan&#355;area\nconsor&#355;iilor administrative se realizeaz&#259; potrivit prevederilor art.\n90, 91 &#351;i 91<sup>3</sup>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Consor&#355;iul administrativ, prin consiliul director ori una sau mai\nmulte unit&#259;&#355;i administrativ-teritoriale membre, pe baza mandatului\nacordat de celelalte unit&#259;&#355;i administrativ-teritoriale membre, poate\nasigura pentru acestea, în exercitarea atribu&#355;iilor men&#355;ionate la\nart. 129 alin. (2) lit. a)-d), urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_544611597\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1606\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_544611597\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)activit&#259;&#355;i de natur&#259; juridic&#259;,\ninclusiv reprezentare în justi&#355;ie, potrivit legii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_283970309\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1605\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_283970309\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)contrasemnarea pentru legalitate a actelor administrative\nemise/adoptate pentru unit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale membre;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1784865391\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1604\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1784865391\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)activit&#259;&#355;i de gestiune a resurselor umane,\ninclusiv salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri publice;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1097929533\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1603\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1097929533\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)activit&#259;&#355;i de natur&#259; financiar&#259;,\ninclusiv administrarea impozitelor &#351;i taxelor locale, cu respectarea\nprevederilor Legii nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>273/2006</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind finan&#355;ele publice locale, cu\nmodific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare, &#351;i &#355;inerea\neviden&#355;ei financiar-contabile;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_558847594\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1602\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_558847594\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)exercitarea controlului financiar preventiv propriu,\nconform reglement&#259;rilor legale în domeniu, pentru unit&#259;&#355;ile\nadministrativ-teritoriale membre;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_207063785\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1601\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_207063785\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)activit&#259;&#355;i de elaborare a documenta&#355;iei de\natribuire &#351;i de derulare a procedurilor de achizi&#355;ii publice,\nînchiriere, concesionare pentru realizarea unor obiective de interes local;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1138313017\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1600\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1138313017\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)activit&#259;&#355;i de elaborare &#351;i/sau avizare a\ndocumenta&#355;iilor de amenajare a teritoriului &#351;i urbanism pentru\nunit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale membre care nu au structuri de\nspecialitate aferente;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_720349742\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1599\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_720349742\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)emiterea certificatelor de urbanism &#351;i a\nautoriza&#355;iilor de construire/desfiin&#355;are, eliberarea avizului\nstructurii de specialitate sau emiterea avizului de oportunitate în vederea\nelabor&#259;rii unui plan urbanistic zonal, dup&#259; caz, pentru\nunit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale membre care nu au structuri de\nspecialitate aferente;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1160046898\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1598\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1160046898\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)activit&#259;&#355;i de elaborare, monitorizare sau\nevaluare de strategii &#351;i alte documente strategice similare în vederea\npromov&#259;rii dezvolt&#259;rii locale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_396727896\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1597\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_396727896\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)activit&#259;&#355;i de ini&#355;iere &#351;i realizare\nde investi&#355;ii în contextul Strategiei de dezvoltare teritorial&#259; a\nRomâniei, Programului na&#355;ional de reforme &#351;i rezilien&#355;&#259; sau\naltor strategii ori programe de finan&#355;are na&#355;ionale sau\ninterna&#355;ionale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2108456378\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1596\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2108456378\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)prestarea de servicii de asisten&#355;&#259;\nsocial&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_240668038\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1595\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_240668038\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>l)activit&#259;&#355;i privind registrul agricol;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1315206167\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1594\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1315206167\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>m)activit&#259;&#355;i de stare civil&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_765261784\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1593\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_765261784\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n)activit&#259;&#355;i care s&#259; faciliteze integrarea\ndigital&#259; a serviciilor publice;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_786182155\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1592\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_786182155\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n<sup>1</sup>)activit&#259;&#355;i privind administrarea\nbunurilor proprietate public&#259; &#351;i privat&#259; a unit&#259;&#355;ilor\nadministrativ-teritoriale membre ale consor&#355;iului administrativ, cu\nrespectarea prevederilor art. 91<sup>4</sup>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1755780360\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1591\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1755780360\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>n<sup>2</sup>)activit&#259;&#355;i de cadastru;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1665313517\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1590\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1665313517\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>o)alte activit&#259;&#355;i.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1835331366\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1589\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1835331366\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>1</sup>)Prin hot&#259;râri ale\nautorit&#259;&#355;ilor deliberative, unit&#259;&#355;ile\nadministrativ-teritoriale pot mandata consor&#355;iul administrativ s&#259;\nangajeze &#351;i s&#259; implementeze, pe seama &#351;i în numele lor, unele\ninvesti&#355;ii care se circumscriu scopului &#351;i obiectivelor\nconsor&#355;iului administrativ, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1250883966\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1588\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1250883966\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2<sup>2</sup>)Prin hot&#259;râri ale\nautorit&#259;&#355;ilor deliberative, unit&#259;&#355;ile\nadministrativ-teritoriale pot mandata consor&#355;iul administrativ s&#259;\nderuleze, pe seama &#351;i în numele lor, unele proceduri de achizi&#355;ii\npublice, care se circumscriu scopului consor&#355;iului administrativ, în\ncondi&#355;iile legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>În statutul consor&#355;iului administrativ, pe lâng&#259; obiectivele\nconsor&#355;iului administrativ, se precizeaz&#259; în mod expres:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_645696088\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1587\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_645696088\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)atribu&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (2) care se\nexercit&#259; în cadrul consor&#355;iului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_102268157\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1586\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_102268157\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)pentru fiecare din atribu&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la\nlit. a) care sunt unit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale beneficiare sau\nprestatoare, dup&#259; caz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1853118307\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1585\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1853118307\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)categoriile de resurse umane alocate pentru exercitarea\nfiec&#259;reia dintre atribu&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la lit. a) de c&#259;tre\nunitatea administrativ-teritorial&#259; prestatoare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_821075963\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1584\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_821075963\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)modul de repartizare între unit&#259;&#355;ile\nadministrativ-teritoriale membre a eventualelor taxe sau tarife colectate de\nc&#259;tre unitatea administrativ-teritorial&#259; prestatoare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2076346166\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1583\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2076346166\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)modalitatea de repartizare a costului cu resursele umane\nutilizate în cadrul consor&#355;iului de c&#259;tre unitatea\nadministrativ-teritorial&#259; prestatoare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_134241897\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1582\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_134241897\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)cuantumul contribu&#355;iilor din bugetele\nunit&#259;&#355;ilor administrativ-teritoriale membre în consor&#355;iul\nadministrativ, în condi&#355;iile art. 90 alin. (1);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1252107615\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1581\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1252107615\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)categoriile de atribu&#355;ii prev&#259;zute la alin. (2)\ncare se asigur&#259; de c&#259;tre consor&#355;iu pentru unele sau toate\nunit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale, membre ale consor&#355;iului\nadministrativ.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>În aplicarea prevederilor alin. (3) lit. c), unit&#259;&#355;ile\nadministrativ-teritoriale pot beneficia de sprijin din partea personalului din\nunit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale prestatoare, nominalizat în\ncondi&#355;iile alin. (7), doar pentru func&#355;iile publice vacante sau\ntemporar vacante pentru o perioad&#259; de cel pu&#355;in 3 luni\ncalendaristice, pentru care sunt îndeplinite cumulativ urm&#259;toarele\ncondi&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1709715496\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1580\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1709715496\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)func&#355;iile publice nu au putut fi ocupate prin una\ndintre modalit&#259;&#355;ile de ocupare prev&#259;zute la art. 466 alin. (2),\nrespectiv art. 615;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_256879415\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1579\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_256879415\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)nu a putut fi dispus&#259; delegarea atribu&#355;iilor\naferente acestora în condi&#355;iile art. 438.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_970310319\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1578\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_970310319\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Prin excep&#355;ie de la prevederile alin. (4),\nunit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale pot beneficia de sprijin din\npartea personalului din unit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale\nprestatoare, nominalizat în condi&#355;iile alin. (7), &#351;i în cazul în care\nvolumul de activitate determin&#259; un grad de înc&#259;rcare a personalului\nacestora de peste 100%, cu excep&#355;ia posturilor unice &#351;i cu încadrarea\nîn cheltuielile de personal aprobate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_591002623\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1577\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_591002623\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)Unit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale membre ale\nunui consor&#355;iu administrativ au obliga&#355;ia organiz&#259;rii\nconcursurilor de recrutare sau promovare pentru func&#355;iile publice\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (4) lit. a), în termen de maximum 2 ani de la emiterea\nactului administrativ prev&#259;zut la alin. (7), în condi&#355;iile legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_349639492\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1576\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_349639492\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)În aplicarea prevederilor alin. (3) lit. c), prin act\nadministrativ comun al autorit&#259;&#355;ilor executive, unitatea\nadministrativ-teritorial&#259; prestatoare &#351;i unitatea\nadministrativ-teritorial&#259; beneficiar&#259;, membre ale unui consor&#355;iu\nadministrativ, nominalizeaz&#259;, cu acordul persoanelor în cauz&#259;, pentru\no perioad&#259; de maximum 2 ani, în func&#355;ie de natura\nactivit&#259;&#355;ii, func&#355;ionari publici sau personal contractual care\ns&#259; îndeplineasc&#259; activit&#259;&#355;i în cadrul consor&#355;iului, în\nexercitarea atribu&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (2).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_184061614\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1575\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_184061614\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Fi&#351;a postului pentru personalul nominalizat în\ncondi&#355;iile alin. (7) se completeaz&#259; cu atribu&#355;iile privind\nactivit&#259;&#355;ile desf&#259;&#351;urate în cadrul consor&#355;iului\n&#351;i devine anex&#259; la actul administrativ comun de nominalizare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1821680815\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1574\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1821680815\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin derogare de la prevederile art. 94 alin. (2) lit.\na) din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>161/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, personalul unit&#259;&#355;ii administrativ-teritoriale\nprestatoare, nominalizat în condi&#355;iile alin. (7), poate îndeplini\nactivit&#259;&#355;i în cadrul consor&#355;iului, în exercitarea atribu&#355;iilor\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (2), pentru unitatea administrativ-teritorial&#259;\nbeneficiar&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1437773290\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1573\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1437773290\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Personalul unit&#259;&#355;ii administrativ-teritoriale\nprestatoare, nominalizat în condi&#355;iile alin. (7), care îndepline&#351;te\nactivit&#259;&#355;i în cadrul consor&#355;iului, în exercitarea\natribu&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (2), pentru unitatea\nadministrativ-teritorial&#259; beneficiar&#259;, are obliga&#355;ia s&#259;\nrespecte prevederile art. 79 din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>161/2003</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile\nulterioare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_697165081\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1572\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_697165081\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(11)Fiecare unitate administrativ-teritorial&#259;\nbeneficiar&#259; acord&#259; personalului din unitatea\nadministrativ-teritorial&#259; prestatoare, nominalizat în condi&#355;iile\nalin. (7), care realizeaz&#259; activit&#259;&#355;i în cadrul consor&#355;iului,\nîn exercitarea atribu&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute la alin. (2), cu respectarea\nlegisla&#355;iei în vigoare referitoare la programul de lucru, o\nindemniza&#355;ie lunar&#259; în valoare de 20% din salariul de baz&#259; de\ncare beneficiaz&#259; persoana nominalizat&#259;, stabilit potrivit legii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1822539627\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1571\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1822539627\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(12)Indemniza&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (11) se\nacord&#259; de la data comunic&#259;rii actului administrativ comun\nprev&#259;zut la alin. (7) &#351;i numai pe perioada în care persoana în\ncauz&#259; desf&#259;&#351;oar&#259; activit&#259;&#355;ile prev&#259;zute în\nacordul de asociere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_182643476\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1570\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_182643476\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(13)Indemniza&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (11) nu\nse ia în calcul la stabilirea limitei prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 11 alin. (4)\ndin Legea-cadru nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>153/2017</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> privind salarizarea personalului pl&#259;tit din fonduri\npublice, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1803393982\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1569\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1803393982\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(14)Asocierea în condi&#355;iile prezentului articolul nu\npoate constitui temei pentru derogare de la condi&#355;iile de studii &#351;i\nvechime necesare a fi îndeplinite de c&#259;tre persoanele care ar ocupa\nfunc&#355;iile publice în unitatea administrativ-teritorial&#259;\nbeneficiar&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1256103194\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1568\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1256103194\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(15)Prevederile alin. (11) nu sunt aplicabile ale&#351;ilor\nlocali.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1774473852\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1567\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1774473852\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(16)Retragerea din consor&#355;iu se notific&#259; tuturor\nmembrilor consor&#355;iului administrativ cu minimum 90 de zile înainte de data\nde 31 decembrie &#351;i devine efectiv&#259; de la data de 1 ianuarie a anului\ncalendaristic urm&#259;tor celui în care s-a f&#259;cut notificarea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1393197246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1566\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1393197246\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(17)Pentru a stimula cooperarea unit&#259;&#355;ilor\nadministrativ-teritoriale în consor&#355;ii administrative, începând cu anul\n2024 se înfiin&#355;eaz&#259; Programul multianual pentru sprijinirea\ncooper&#259;rii unit&#259;&#355;ilor administrativ-teritoriale membre ale\nconsor&#355;iilor administrative, a c&#259;rui finan&#355;are este\nasigurat&#259; de la bugetul de stat, prin bugetul Ministerului\nDezvolt&#259;rii, Lucr&#259;rilor Publice &#351;i Administra&#355;iei.\nCreditele de angajament &#351;i creditele bugetare se prev&#259;d prin legea\nbugetului de stat. Finan&#355;area se asigur&#259; pe baza unor criterii de\nperforman&#355;&#259; transparente care se circumscriu obiectivelor\nprev&#259;zute la art. 89 alin. (8<sup>4</sup>).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2042065959\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1565\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2042065959\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(18)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Programul\nmultianual pentru sprijinirea cooper&#259;rii unit&#259;&#355;ilor\nadministrativ-teritoriale membre ale consor&#355;iilor administrative va avea\nurm&#259;toarele obiective:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1347080060\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1564\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1347080060\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)func&#355;ionarea consor&#355;iilor administrative;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2071997255\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1563\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2071997255\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)integrarea digital&#259; a serviciilor publice furnizate\nde unit&#259;&#355;ile administrativ-teritoriale, membre ale consor&#355;iilor\nadministrative, în vederea furniz&#259;rii de servicii publice într-un timp mai\nscurt pentru cet&#259;&#355;eni &#351;i antreprenori.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_624983701\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1562\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Cod%20Administrativ.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_624983701\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(19)Descrierea Programului multianual pentru sprijinirea\ncooper&#259;rii unit&#259;&#355;ilor administrativ-teritoriale membre ale\nconsor&#355;iilor administrative se aprob&#259; prin hot&#259;râre a\nGuvernului, la propunerea ministerului cu atribu&#355;ii în domeniul\nadministra&#355;iei publice.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}